@namespace PgmStudio.Client.Pages.AuthoringParts
@using PgmStudio.Client.Pages.EditorActivities

@* Teams (02) — three sub-steps: (1) team creation + island assignment, (2) spawn point, (3) spawn
   protection. Spawn points and protection rectangles are separate steps with separate lists, so each
   inspector shows only the relevant region. Canvas = thunder's REAL islands (IslandMap Mode="teams"). *@

<section class="ds-section" id="teams">
  <div class="ds-section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="ds-kicker">02</p>
      <h2>Teams &amp; Spawns</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Three sub-steps — create the teams and assign islands (fixing the orbit order), then place team 0's
       spawn point, then its protection zone. Orbit fills the rest; protection is auto-wired.</p>
  </div>

  <p class="ds-theming-note">
    Symmetry suggests the team count; the author tags islands to teams as <strong>authoring help</strong>
    — this fixes the <em>orbit order</em> (the sequence the map was laid out in) and seats each spawn on
    the right island. Islands are neutral by default — not every island needs a team. Thunder's centre
    island stays <strong>contested</strong>. Authors often colour-code islands with clay or wool; the
    assignment mirrors that intent. Spawn point and protection are separate steps so each inspector shows
    just the relevant region.
  </p>

  <div class="ds-sug-sample" style="max-width:320px;margin:var(--space-4) 0">
    <SmartSuggestion Header="Smart Suggestion" Badge="rot 90" AcceptLabel="Create 4 teams" RejectLabel="Dismiss">
      <p class="smart-suggestion__text">90° rotational symmetry suggests four teams.</p>
      <div class="smart-suggestion-teams">
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#5555FF"></span>Blue Team</div>
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#FF5555"></span>Red Team</div>
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#55FF55"></span>Green Team</div>
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#FFFF55"></span>Yellow Team</div>
      </div>
    </SmartSuggestion>
  </div>

  <div class="ds-steps">

  @* ── Step 1 · Team creation + island assignment ────────────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Step 1 of 3 — Teams &amp; island assignment</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="users"></i><span>Teams</span></div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Teams &amp; islands</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Spawn point</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Protection</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn" disabled>Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Next: Spawn point</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
      <div class="workspace">
        <div class="workspace-sidebar">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Teams</h2></div>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--selected"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">blue</span><span class="badge badge--success">authored</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#55FF55"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">green</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FF5555"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">red</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FFFF55"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">yellow</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                <h2 class="section-title">Island Assignment</h2>
                <span class="badge badge--dim">authoring help</span>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="layers"></i></span><span class="list-label">Centre island</span><span class="badge badge--dim">contested</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><span class="list-label">West islands</span><span class="list-tag">blue ×4</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#55FF55"></span><span class="list-label">East islands</span><span class="list-tag">green ×4</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FF5555"></span><span class="list-label">South islands</span><span class="list-tag">red ×4</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FFFF55"></span><span class="list-label">North islands</span><span class="list-tag">yellow ×4</span></div>
              </div>
              <p class="section-desc">Tagging islands tints them and fixes the orbit order. Untagged islands stay neutral — the centre is contested.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Team Size &amp; Kit</h2></div>
              <div class="section-body">
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Max Players <span class="list-tag">all teams</span></label><input class="field-input" type="number" value="12"/></div>
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Spawn Kit</label><select class="field-input"><option selected>spawn-kit</option></select></div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-canvas">
          <div class="canvas-subbar">
            <div class="canvas-toolbar">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Pan"><i data-lucide="hand"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Select"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="subbar-sep"></div>
            <button class="filter-chip filter-chip--active" title="Orbit fill active">Orbit</button>
            <span class="canvas-cursor">X -93 · Z -15</span>
            <div class="canvas-subbar-right">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Fit island"><i data-lucide="maximize-2"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Reset zoom"><i data-lucide="scan"></i></button>
              <span class="canvas-zoom">100%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="canvas-surface canvas-surface--svg">
            <IslandMap Mode="teams" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-inspector">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="detail-header">
                <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="users"></i></span>
                <span class="detail-label detail-label--mono">blue</span>
                <span class="badge badge--success">authored</span>
              </div>
              <div class="section-body">
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Name</label><input class="field-input" value="Blue"/></div>
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Colour</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="field-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><select class="field-input"><option selected>Blue</option></select></div></div>
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Islands</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="badge badge--neutral">4</span><span class="list-tag">west quadrant</span></div></div>
                <p class="section-desc">Orbit position 0. Green, red, and yellow follow by 90° rotation.</p>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  @* ── Step 2 · Spawn point ──────────────────────────────────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Step 2 of 3 — Spawn point</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="users"></i><span>Teams</span></div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Teams &amp; islands</button>
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Spawn point</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Protection</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn">Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Next: Protection</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
      <div class="workspace">
        <div class="workspace-sidebar">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Spawn Points</h2></div>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--selected"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">blue-spawn</span><span class="badge badge--success">authored</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">green-spawn</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">red-spawn</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">yellow-spawn</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
              </div>
              <p class="section-desc">Place team 0's spawn point; the orbit derives the other three. Protection is the next step.</p>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-canvas">
          <div class="canvas-subbar">
            <div class="canvas-toolbar">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Pan"><i data-lucide="hand"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Select"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Place spawn point"><i data-lucide="dot"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="subbar-sep"></div>
            <button class="filter-chip filter-chip--active" title="Orbit fill active">Orbit</button>
            <span class="canvas-cursor">X -93 · Z -15</span>
            <div class="canvas-subbar-right">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Fit island · Blue"><i data-lucide="maximize-2"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Reset zoom"><i data-lucide="scan"></i></button>
              <span class="canvas-zoom">230%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="canvas-surface canvas-surface--svg">
            <IslandMap Mode="teams">
              <circle cx="34.5" cy="112.5" r="2.8" fill="#5555FF" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.8" />
              <circle cx="222.5" cy="144.5" r="2.2" fill="#55FF55" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6" />
              <circle cx="112.5" cy="222.5" r="2.2" fill="#FF5555" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6" />
              <circle cx="144.5" cy="34.5" r="2.2" fill="#FFFF55" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6" />
            </IslandMap>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-inspector">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="detail-header">
                <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="cylinder"></i></span>
                <span class="detail-label detail-label--mono">blue-spawn</span>
                <span class="badge badge--neutral">Cylinder</span>
              </div>
              <div class="section-body">
                <div class="field">
                  <label class="field-label">Base</label>
                  <div class="ctrl-row">
                    <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">X</span><input class="coord-input" value="-93.5"/></div>
                    <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">Y</span><input class="coord-input" value="7"/></div>
                    <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">Z</span><input class="coord-input" value="-15.5"/></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                  <label class="field-label">Radius / Height / Yaw</label>
                  <div class="ctrl-row">
                    <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">R</span><input class="coord-input" value="1"/></div>
                    <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">H</span><input class="coord-input" value="0"/></div>
                    <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">°</span><input class="coord-input" value="0"/></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                  <div class="slice-head">
                    <label class="field-label">Side view — drag the line to set Y</label>
                    <div class="slice-axis">
                      <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Inspect from −Z">Z−</button>
                      <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Inspect from +Z">Z+</button>
                      <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Inspect from −X">X−</button>
                      <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Inspect from +X">X+</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="slice-view" style="position:relative">
                    <canvas class="slice-canvas"></canvas>
                    <span style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:47%;height:2px;background:var(--accent);opacity:.85;pointer-events:none"></span>
                    <span style="position:absolute;right:6px;top:36%;font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;pointer-events:none">Y 7</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  @* ── Step 3 · Spawn protection ─────────────────────────────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Step 3 of 3 — Spawn protection</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-bar-phase"><i data-lucide="users"></i><span>Teams</span></div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Teams &amp; islands</button>
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--done"><i data-lucide="check"></i>Spawn point</button>
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Protection</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn">Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Next: Build</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
      <div class="workspace">
        <div class="workspace-sidebar">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                <h2 class="section-title">Protection</h2>
                <button class="action-btn">+ Add</button>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--selected"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">blue-spawn-protect</span><span class="badge badge--success">authored</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">green-spawn-protect</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">red-spawn-protect</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">yellow-spawn-protect</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
              </div>
              <p class="section-desc">Draw a protection rectangle around the spawn; orbit derives the rest. Each is auto-wired with an enter filter.</p>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-canvas">
          <div class="canvas-subbar">
            <div class="canvas-toolbar">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Pan"><i data-lucide="hand"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Select"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Draw protection rectangle"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="subbar-sep"></div>
            <button class="filter-chip filter-chip--active" title="Orbit fill active">Orbit</button>
            <span class="canvas-cursor">X -90 · Z -15</span>
            <div class="canvas-subbar-right">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Fit island · Blue"><i data-lucide="maximize-2"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Reset zoom"><i data-lucide="scan"></i></button>
              <span class="canvas-zoom">230%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="canvas-surface canvas-surface--svg">
            <IslandMap Mode="teams">
              @* protection rectangles (blue selected/bright, others orbit) + faint spawn points *@
              <rect x="29" y="107" width="18" height="12" rx="1" fill="color-mix(in oklch,#5555FF 14%,transparent)" stroke="#5555FF" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2 1.5" />
              <rect x="210" y="138" width="18" height="12" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="#55FF55" stroke-width="0.7" stroke-dasharray="2 1.5" opacity="0.55" />
              <rect x="107" y="210" width="12" height="18" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="#FF5555" stroke-width="0.7" stroke-dasharray="2 1.5" opacity="0.55" />
              <rect x="138" y="29" width="12" height="18" rx="1" fill="none" stroke="#FFFF55" stroke-width="0.7" stroke-dasharray="2 1.5" opacity="0.55" />
              <circle cx="34.5" cy="112.5" r="2" fill="#5555FF" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.8" />
              <circle cx="222.5" cy="144.5" r="1.8" fill="#55FF55" opacity="0.4" />
              <circle cx="112.5" cy="222.5" r="1.8" fill="#FF5555" opacity="0.4" />
              <circle cx="144.5" cy="34.5" r="1.8" fill="#FFFF55" opacity="0.4" />
            </IslandMap>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-inspector">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <div class="panel-stack">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="detail-header">
                  <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="rectangle-horizontal"></i></span>
                  <span class="detail-label detail-label--mono">blue-spawn-protect</span>
                  <span class="badge badge--neutral">Rectangle</span>
                </div>
                <div class="section-body">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label class="field-label">Min</label>
                    <div class="ctrl-row">
                      <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">X</span><input class="coord-input" value="-99"/></div>
                      <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">Z</span><input class="coord-input" value="-21"/></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label class="field-label">Max</label>
                    <div class="ctrl-row">
                      <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">X</span><input class="coord-input" value="-81"/></div>
                      <div class="coord-field"><span class="coord-prefix">Z</span><input class="coord-input" value="-9"/></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <div class="slice-head">
                      <label class="field-label">Side view — terrain under the zone</label>
                      <div class="slice-axis">
                        <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Inspect from −Z">Z−</button>
                        <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Inspect from +Z">Z+</button>
                        <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Inspect from −X">X−</button>
                        <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Inspect from +X">X+</button>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="slice-view" style="position:relative">
                      <canvas class="slice-canvas"></canvas>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Auto-wiring</h2>
                  <span class="badge badge--dim">derived</span>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-list">
                  <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--muted"><span class="geo-type-icon"><i data-lucide="link"></i></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">enter = only-blue</span><span class="list-tag">spawn protect</span></div>
                </div>
                <p class="section-desc">Message “You may not enter the enemy's spawn!”. Orbit replicates the protection + wiring for green, red, and yellow.</p>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  </div>
</section>
